</FONT>
<HR size="1" color="#dedfdf">
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
"But for some ODD reason you forget the disadvantage... mainly everyone gets levitation around 12th-16th level... Magician gets it at 29th level."<P>Incidentally Wizards get Levitate at level... (drum roll please)... 24.  <P>Guess when Wizards get invisibility?  16th level.  Mages get invis at level 8.  <P>See how this works?  We can do this all day back and forth.  Different classes get different spells at different levels.  Why Verant did it I can only guess at, but some of the logic is truly mystifying.<P>Levitate Rings are better than levitate spells, sorry if you don't care to believe that but its flat out a fact.  Is the level high?  Yeah its stupidly high, but look at how high the no-reagent levitate spell is in Luclin.<P>--------------------<P>===================================<P>        Grimstaff Theurgist<P>===================================
</FONT>
